            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I think I have noticed about this for a while, but not sure what is the problem.\n\nI'm using oxlint lsp in a project. And when I'm in insert mode, typing (faster than the debounce option set), exit to normal mode, the language server sends quite many diagnostics (incrementally) to neovim until it is up to date with current changes of the buffer.\n\nCurrently, I'm ignored it for now, till I see this issue.",
